-1- - poetry run python manage.py

Create django project: django-admin startproject <project name> [.]
Run server: -1- runserver

Create application: -1- startapp <app name>

Generate model based on existing database: -1- inspectdb <tables name>
[--database <db name>] [--include views] [--include partitions]


Create migrations: -1- makemigrations <app name>
Run migration: -1- migrate [app name [migration module name]]
Check migration SQL commands: -1- sqlmigrate <app name> <migration module name>
[--database <db name>] [--backwards]
Show list of migrations: -1- showmigrations [app names] [--database <db name>] [--plan|-p]
Optimize migration: -1- optimizemigration <app name> <migration module name> [--check]
Merge migrations: -1- squashmigrations <app name> [first migration module name] <last migration module name>
[--squashed_name <result migration module name>] [--no-optimize] [--noinput|--no-input] [--no-header]
Flush database: -1- flush [--database <db name>] [--noinput|--no-input]
Check flush migration SQL commands: -1- sqlflush [--database <db name>]
Cancel migration: -1- migrate [app name [not cancelled migration module name]]
Cancel all migrations: -1- migrate [app name zero]

Run django shell: -1- shell
Close django shell: exit()

Create superuser for admin website: -1- createsuperuser